    public abstract class AbstractServiceLoaderBasedFactoryBean
extends AbstractFactoryBean<java.lang.Object>

    Abstract base class for FactoryBeans operating on the JDK 1.6 ServiceLoader facility.

    2.5
    作者:
    Juergen Hoeller

      • setBeanClassLoader

        public void setBeanClassLoader(@Nullable
                               java.lang.ClassLoader beanClassLoader)
        从接口复制的说明: BeanClassLoaderAware
        Callback that supplies the bean class loader to a bean instance.

        Invoked after the population of normal bean properties but before an initialization callback such as InitializingBean's InitializingBean.afterPropertiesSet() method or a custom init-method.

        指定者:
        setBeanClassLoader 在接口中 BeanClassLoaderAware
        覆盖:
        setBeanClassLoader 在类中 AbstractFactoryBean<java.lang.Object>
        参数:
        beanClassLoader - the owning class loader
